snippet.title: Story of Seasons: A Wonderful Life - Official Gameplay Overview Trailer | Wholesome Direct 2023
snippet.description: Take a look at character customization, new facilities, new hybrid crops, and more in this latest trailer for Story of Seasons: A Wonderful Life. Story of Seasons: A Wonderful Life, the upcoming remake of the farming and life sim classic game, will be available on Windows PC via Steam, PlayStation 5, Xbox Series X/S, and Nintendo Switch on June 27, 2023.
